This is a time where you will find yourself drawing strength from those around you. Your need for self-expression will be great and your efforts to show the world your abilities and talents will draw the kind of people you need around you closer. You will find yourself reaching out to people and championing causes that you will lend your creative hand (or feet, or voice, or words) to. Choose those causes wisely or you might burn out. Your energy will be very positive and effervescent. Use it in ways that exalt and uplift.
